rows.label: qst710601_msg0001
rows.name:
Mo... I'm so hungry, mo...
The portions at this place
are way too small, mo...

rows.label: qst710601_msg0002
rows.name:
Hm? You need something
from Morimori, mo?

rows.label: qst710601_msg0003
rows.name:
Morimori is eating right now,
mo. Come back later, mo.

rows.label: qst710601_msg0004
rows.name:
...Mo? Wait, mo. Do you
happen to have any food, mo?

rows.label: qst710601_msg0005
rows.name:
Morimori is having trouble
because the food at this
place is not enough, mo.

rows.label: qst710601_msg0006
rows.name:
If you have any food or dishes,
please share them with Morimori, mo!

rows.label: qst710601_msg0007
rows.name:
Morimori happen to be one of
best gourmets out of all Nopon!

rows.label: qst710601_msg0008
rows.name:
I can't accept any food unless
it makes my tongue tingle, mo!

rows.label: qst710601_msg0009
rows.name:
Well then, I'm looking
forward to it, mo!
